Package org.apache.wiki.rss

Class Summary
AtomFeed Provides an Atom 1.0 standard feed, with enclosures.
Entry Represents an entry, that is, an unit of change, in a Feed.
Feed Represents an abstract feed.
RSS10Feed Provides an implementation of an RSS 1.0 feed.
RSS20Feed Represents an RSS 2.0 feed (with enclosures).
RSSGenerator The master class for generating different kinds of Feeds (including RSS1.0, 2.0 and Atom).
RSSThread Runs the RSS generation thread.
